item.description: I am a bioinformatics bachelor student at the Technical University of Munich and the Ludwig-Maximilians-University. Since October 2020, I am an intern at the Chair of Experimental Bioinformatics to gain more practical experience in bioinformatics. Currently I am working for Markus Hoffmann on the development of GenEpiSeeker, a tool for generic epistasis detection via local search.
